          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on data from United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (comtrade.un.org). UN comtrade category: 293020 Thiocarbamates and dithiocarbamates. Year 2005. Using exchange rate of 1EURO = 1.209 USD. Average of price of import into 5 main markets (EU, US, JP, IN and CN).</comment>
